definition: Yun county in Shiyan 十堰[Shi2 yan4], Hubei

sentences.english: Tanshan Town of Yun County is abundant in marble resource.
sentences.chinese: 鄖縣譚山鎮大理石資源豐富。

sentences.english: The second chapter describes the phonology transfer system of Yunxian dialect.
sentences.chinese: 第二章描寫鄖縣方言的聲韻調系統。

sentences.english: A large amount of Dinosaurs skeleton fossils are discovered in Upper Cretaceous strata at the Meipu Town, Yunxian County of Hubei Province.
sentences.chinese: 湖北省鄖縣梅鋪鎮晚白堊世地層中發現大量恐龍化石。

sentences.english: You can visit the site of dinosaur eggs fossils at Mt. Qinglong in Yunxian County.
sentences.chinese: 你可以去參觀鄖縣青龍山恐龍蛋化石。

sentences.english: You can try three delicacies soup, Yunxian style.
sentences.chinese: 你可以嚐嚐鄖縣三合湯。
